{"tid":277463,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[新機落地]究竟壞咩撚野...","createTime":"2017-06-09T15:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T09:06:41.000Z","uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c630435e391778cc78b38b18c51a6dc23fb3094","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:10:18.000Z","msg":"WD Blue WD10EZEX 1TB 7200rpm 64MB 3.5 Inch HDD<br />\nSamsung 960 EVO Series - 250GB PCIe NVMe - M.2 SSD<br />\nAntec NeoEco II Series NEO-ECO2-550 80Plus Bronze 550W PSU<br />\nMSI GeForce&reg; GTX 1070 GAMING X 8GB GDDR5<br />\nCorsair VENGEANCE&reg; LED 16GB (2 x 8GB) DDR4 3000MHz C15 - White LED<br />\nAMD RYZEN R7 1700 3.7GHz 16M L3 8 Core 16 Thread 65W AM4<br />\nGigabyte GA-AB350M-Gaming 3 AM4 M.ATX<br />\nWIN10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩OW, DS3, NIER, 全部冇問題,MAX SETTING 都KEEP住60FPS.<br />\n<br />\n玩THE SURGE 會無啦啦LAG, 背景聲(風聲/音樂)或者講緊的對白完全唔受影響,連D水聲風聲都唔會停,剩係人物同敵人暫停幾秒,全部較做LOW 完全冇改善冇影響,但係LAG個幾秒GPU LOAD 同埋GPU MEMORY CONTROLLER 會變0%,之後變番正常50-70%<br />\n<br />\n另外如果用OBS 錄影(剩錄唔直播都一樣問題),上面講的OW,DS3,NIER 係GAME入面都完全冇問題一樣KEEP住60FPS, 但係出黎個條片會同THE SURGE 個隻GAME 一樣會無啦啦LAG幾秒,又係聲音完全冇影響,剩係畫面會LAG幾秒<br />\n<br />\nOBS 到較SETTING都完全冇影響,60&gt;30FPS, ENCODER PRESET由ULTRA FAST 轉到SLOWER 完全冇可見影響,唔係好覺LAG得密左,唔覺LAG得耐左,GAME入面都較全低SETTING, CAP FPS 60, 一樣係唔覺LAG得密左,唔覺LAG得耐左<br />\n<br />\nOBS 個STATS到寫係Skipped Frames due to encoding lag 個到會唔見FRAME, Frames missed due to rendering lag 一直係0,即是係ENCODING 有問題<br />\n<br />\n錄影時CPU 係5-10%, GPU LOAD 冇試過超過75%<br />\n<br />\n試過2條RAM 插去另一SET RAM 槽,冇分別,試過插1條RAM, 2條都試過單行,冇分別, 更新左DISPLAY DRIVER, 更新埋WINDOWS, 關左GAME MODE, 加哂落防毒EXCLUDE, 所有野試過都完全冇分別....直情連令佢惡化好轉都唔得......<br />\n<br />\n攪左成個星期完全唔知係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會係CPU或者張DISPLAY本身有問題? 定係其他原因?"},{"pid":"dba0a5534bdfaf7a7b0d8ded27bed553233e2b0b","tid":277463,"uid":65092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:24:49.000Z","msg":"睇晒 但無能為力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3370f24d6e9713762d55e137c8ac1f81820e8c1a","tid":277463,"uid":72,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"睇你咁樣應該咩方法都試過<br />\n借朋友張顯示卡試下<br />\n唯有由顯示卡&gt;cpu逐件逐件試下"},{"pid":"5509a0d1fae490d749fbc6f03898f90134ccd679","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你咁樣應該咩方法都試過<br />\n借朋友張顯示卡試下<br />\n唯有由顯示卡&gt;cpu逐件逐件試下</blockquote><br />\n呢塊板插唔插到AMD R9 270X(舊機個張)? <br />\n<br />\n不過插到都要重裝哂DRIVER先試到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0142dc025ef0868accfd221c61e84d323164d98","tid":277463,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"應該是ram 同bois  問題<br />\n試重置bois"},{"pid":"089b9bcee9496451f4a3f732e559d4cf0541b2a4","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該是ram 同bois  問題<br />\n試重置bois</blockquote><br />\n即係入BIOS RESET TO DEFAULT?"},{"pid":"c263e1000f63d80f8de2f0aba094f28996fede1e","tid":277463,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"你先同朋友借張display card 測試D 硬件先 <br />\n之後 再搞bois同ram"},{"pid":"32a30be3fa3f1b19fae940124a675607c8a65337","tid":277463,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"試下入nvidia 度 -&gt;管理3D設定-&gt;電源管理模式 轉做慣用最大效能"},{"pid":"45cbf5b821bd23cc2a2942a4c50d89c9b27c8576","tid":277463,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"試下入nvidia 度 -&gt;管理3D設定-&gt;電源管理模式 轉做慣用最大效能"},{"pid":"17b4c797b1f3298bfce782f4668f46e95521a1ca","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下入nvidia 度 -&gt;管理3D設定-&gt;電源管理模式 轉做慣用最大效能</blockquote><br />\n呢個冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d4c0ba7962da0eceadf5c0a734c5527d276080","tid":277463,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"你試下較低隻game 既resolution<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得係優化問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f443a026097577e702f575d5a3fc0b4faa19bb57","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你試下較低隻game 既resolution<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得係優化問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe Surge 點較都LAG,錄片就GAME同OBS點較都完全冇可見的分別,由最高較到最低都冇分別"},{"pid":"66ea1bc5cf418314be22477677c6a5d8db246762","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你試下較低隻game 既resolution<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得係優化問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe Surge 點較都LAG,錄片就GAME同OBS點較都完全冇可見的分別,由最高較到最低都冇分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點係隻GAME同錄片我舊機用AMD R9 270X 都唔會無啦啦LAG同錄片冇問題<br />\n<br />\n而家新機係點SET都冇分別,ULTRA 到LOW 全部冇分別,所以一定係有某D野出左問題"},{"pid":"afc6fe40064c5dd4f6941fefe0e11dbd0ce05b72","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你先同朋友借張display card 測試D 硬件先 <br />\n之後 再搞bois同ram</blockquote><br />\nD FD 唔打機冇張卡係新卡黎.........."},{"pid":"cc94d128ee830d8784a6eca073555bfc50d2416c","tid":277463,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"試多幾隻高低需求既game<br />\n<br />\n如果都無問題<br />\n<br />\n咁應該係隻game問題<br />\n<br />\n搵下有冇一批人玩呢隻game又係lag"},{"pid":"b6f5078c3b37b8b6d58bd2fbe4e45be5a7415cbe","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試多幾隻高低需求既game<br />\n<br />\n如果都無問題<br />\n<br />\n咁應該係隻game問題<br />\n<br />\n搵下有冇一批人玩呢隻game又係lag</blockquote><br />\n得一隻game有事而且唔係重點，重點係錄片我錄條youtube片出黎個file都係會lag，只係隻game係同一個lag法我先估係同源頭/同原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw....我拆哂display背版鑼絲，個鎖按落去張卡彈左少少出黎，但係拔唔到張卡出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d7899676d52daaace7f4ca3efa4c03d7c6d8b7","tid":277463,"uid":65092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試多幾隻高低需求既game<br />\n<br />\n如果都無問題<br />\n<br />\n咁應該係隻game問題<br />\n<br />\n搵下有冇一批人玩呢隻game又係lag</blockquote><br />\n得一隻game有事而且唔係重點，重點係錄片我錄條youtube片出黎個file都係會lag，只係隻game係同一個lag法我先估係同源頭/同原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw....我拆哂display背版鑼絲，個鎖按落去張卡彈左少少出黎，但係拔唔到張卡出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大力d 由左面蚊起"},{"pid":"30100658aff5e2b1da4242f3aea6c2c597c56244","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試多幾隻高低需求既game<br />\n<br />\n如果都無問題<br />\n<br />\n咁應該係隻game問題<br />\n<br />\n搵下有冇一批人玩呢隻game又係lag</blockquote><br />\n得一隻game有事而且唔係重點，重點係錄片我錄條youtube片出黎個file都係會lag，只係隻game係同一個lag法我先估係同源頭/同原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw....我拆哂display背版鑼絲，個鎖按落去張卡彈左少少出黎，但係拔唔到張卡出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大力d 由左面蚊起</blockquote>即係背版個邊?2邊我都蚊唔郁，張卡已經鬆左，但左右都好似卡住，我怕蚊爆野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61a082f367e0e9661bd7059e018b97aea9b8c27","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ErivC8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FErivC8d.jpg&h=921c01da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6572c0f5817af3a5b0e4548a45553758b6a74ae6","tid":277463,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"OK, 用舊機張AMD R9 280X 一樣有呢D問題<br />\n<br />\n唯一分別係張舊卡係隻GAME LAG 個陣個GPU LOAD 唔會趺去0,佢會KEEP 住原先差唔多的LOAD, 但係CPU LOAD 同樣會趺去接近0,其實野冇可見分別(GAME較哂LOW SETTING) <br />\n<br />\n咁而家基本上排除左RAM同DISPLAY問題 (除非2條RAM壞埋同一樣野)<br />\n<br />\n即係軟件/CPU 問題?  CPU我真心唔識拆同裝.....仲要唔知粒舊U 岩唔岩裝 (AMD FX8320)"},{"pid":"8c2459cb18bbc6910880e784a89d0c0844df9681","tid":277463,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ErivC8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FErivC8d.jpg&h=921c01da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset